<td valign="top" align="left" style="border-left: solid 5px #f0f0f0;;padding:0px 5px 0px 15px;">




<strong>Boxset/Compilation, released in 1980</strong><br><br>

<strong>Songs / Tracks Listing</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">1. Black Night (3:23)<br>2. Speed King (5:01)<br>3. Fireball (3:22)<br>4. Strange Kind Of Woman (3:47)<br>5. Child In Time (10:10)<br>6. Woman From Tokyo (5:47)<br>7. Highway Star (6:05)<br>8. Space Truckin' (4:31)<br>9. Burn (6:00)<br>10. Stormbringer (4:05)<br>11. Demon's Eye (5:20)<br>12. Smoke On The Water (5:40)<br><br>Total Time 63:11</p>

<strong>Line-up / Musicians</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">- Ritchie Blackmore / guitars<br>- Ian Paice / drums<br>- Jon Lord / keyboards<br>- Ian Gillan / vocals (1-8,11,12)<br>- Roger Glover / bass (1-8,11,12)<br>- David Coverdale / vocals (9,10)<br>- Glenn Hughes / bass, vocals (9,10)</p>

<strong>Releases information</strong>
<p style="padding-left:5px;">
LP EMI/Harvest (1980)<br>CD EMI/ Harvest CDP 7 46032 2
</p>


